    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a basic set of wheels to get you from A to B? This vehicle is priced to move and ready for someone handy who can give it the TLC it needs! While it has significant wear and tear and shows its age throughout, it offers a great opportunity for a mechanic's special or a low-cost entry into vehicle ownership. Grab a bargain and make this car your next weekend project!",
