    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition and has been meticulously preserved to look and drive like it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, free of any chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin is immaculate, with the leather upholstery still firm and the original factory scent preserved. Mechanically, it is perfect, having followed a rigorous maintenance schedule with all service records available. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that shows zero signs of wear and performs exactly as intended by the manufacturer.",
