      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor dents, and some fading on the paint. The interior shows moderate wear, including some thinning of the upholstery. All mechanical systems are functional but show age-appropriate wear.",
      "price": 22000.0,
